Generic single-database configuration for Slack Event Manager.

This directory contains Alembic migrations for the PostgreSQL database schema.

## Running Migrations

### Development
```bash
# Upgrade to latest
alembic upgrade head

# Downgrade one revision
alembic downgrade -1

# Show current revision
alembic current

# Show migration history
alembic history --verbose
```

### Docker
Migrations run automatically via docker-entrypoint.sh when using PostgreSQL.

## Creating New Migrations

```bash
# Auto-generate migration from model changes
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

# Create empty migration
alembic revision -m "description"
```

## Configuration

Database connection details are loaded from Settings (config.yaml + .env).
See alembic/env.py for configuration logic.

